Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.30,2:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, we will be addressed by Sakura Gakuin Principal Kuramoto Mitsuru
Dialogue: 0,2:04:23.29,2:04:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it has become Sakura season.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:27.29,2:04:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Sakura bloom, it is time for Sakura Gakuin's graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:32.40,2:04:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sakura bloomed about five days early this year.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:39.87,2:04:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But even if the Sakura bloom started, it doesn't feel like it's getting warmer.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:50.21,2:04:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sakura are not really blooming, with only a few just starting to bloom.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:57.68,2:05:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like those flowers, it feels like you are graduating too early
Dialogue: 0,2:05:01.57,2:05:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone probably feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:07.74,2:05:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot to think about.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.91,2:05:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The three graduating this year don't lose to their seniors at all in being interesting.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:19.38,2:05:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Shirai Saki was a Fukei!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.98,2:05:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She is a fan of Sakura Gakuin.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.21,2:05:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A Fukei became a member of Sakura Gakuin
Dialogue: 0,2:05:32.31,2:05:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a miracle for her, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:37.70,2:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Her dream came true at her age!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.29,2:05:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I worried how someone would be motivated after getting her dream.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:46.35,2:05:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She had to overcome such a special situation.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.33,2:05:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There was surely a type of pressure that only Shirai would understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.09,2:06:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She overcame that and did really well as the Talk Chairperson. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:03.81,2:06:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,About the timing for when Ooga Saki transferred in...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:09.61,2:06:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was right after the 1st class graduated.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:13.52,2:06:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the 1st class had been the cardinal members of Sakura Gakuin,
Dialogue: 0,2:06:16.91,2:06:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we worried about what would happen to Sakura Gakuin after they left.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.13,2:06:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We were nervous and tried different things.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:26.98,2:06:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrounded in that environment, not even knowing left from right...
Dialogue: 0,2:06:32.51,2:06:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you were tested in many different ways.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:36.65,2:06:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like you went along even though I didn't know which way to go.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:43.73,2:06:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a lot of guts.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:46.04,2:06:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I think you worried about many things,
Dialogue: 0,2:06:51.56,2:06:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like you gritted your teeth and overcame.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.31,2:06:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:59.05,2:07:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Isono Rinon...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:02.57,2:07:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the only one in all of Sakura Gakuin, the ONLY one,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:08.33,2:07:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,who has experienced everything from since Sakura Gakuin became a school until now. The only one.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:17.66,2:07:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You were there even during my first nightmare class.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:21.55,2:07:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a terrible experience, really.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:23.53,2:07:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You were just sitting there spacing out. "Is she okay?!"
Dialogue: 0,2:07:27.23,2:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, "Is she alive?!"
Dialogue: 0,2:07:29.03,2:07:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I also thought, "Is she a living thing"
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.49,2:07:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, you have experienced everything
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.64,2:07:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was worried about having you become the Student Council president.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.30,2:07:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But we decided to let you do it
Dialogue: 0,2:07:50.44,2:07:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and after just one year, it is surprising how much you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:56.06,2:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You really got yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.53,2:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that speech just now?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:01.69,2:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Without making many mistakes,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.74,2:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:06.97,2:08:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a long speech.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:11.49,2:08:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the content of the speech,
Dialogue: 0,2:08:13.92,2:08:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how other idols do it, but they write these themselves!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:19.20,2:08:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the type of thing that makes me believe Sakura Gakuin is raising Super Ladies.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:26.99,2:08:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you want to be a theater director after you graduate.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.57,2:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:35.97,2:08:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder, how did you become so mature?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:39.20,2:08:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to become Super by supporting others. I think that is great!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:43.92,2:08:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please debut by working with Sakura Gakuin.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.74,2:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After about 5 years?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:52.67,2:08:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:58.46,2:09:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura Gakuin is indeed a school.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:02.66,2:09:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A school to help people become Super.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:08.52,2:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You will all graduate, whatever path you choose
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.16,2:09:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Isono wants to be a director
Dialogue: 0,2:09:15.06,2:09:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think you two should continue thinking about your future,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.90,2:09:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think no matter which genre you go to
Dialogue: 0,2:09:22.44,2:09:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that those who have graduated from Sakura Gakuin
Dialogue: 0,2:09:28.90,2:09:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,will be looked at as Super people.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.25,2:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you will be the center of happiness for many people.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:39.40,2:09:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, without a doubt!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:41.69,2:09:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the former graduates are now gonna be that.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:45.77,2:09:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So believe in yourself and have confidence.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.28,2:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And fry ... uh I mean fly to the future! In the end, I made a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:55.50,2:09:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost to Isono!
Dialogue: 0,2:10:00.02,2:10:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
